Definition.WordDefinition: Fifteen \Fif"teen`\, a. [OE. fiftene, AS. f[=i]ft[=y]ne, f[=i]ft[=e]ne. See {Five}, and {Ten}, and cf. {Fifty}.] Five and ten; one more than fourteen. [1913 Webster]

Dictionary.Name: The Collaborative International Dictionary of English v.0.44

Definition.WordDefinition:
Fifteen \Fif"teen`\, n. 1. The sum of five and ten; fifteen units or objects. [1913 Webster]
2. A symbol representing fifteen units, as 15, or xv. [1913 Webster]
fifteen adj : being one more than fourteen [syn: {15}, {xv}] n : the cardinal number that is the sum of fourteen and one [syn: {15}, {XV}]
